Indoor/Outdoor Usage
Outdoor
  • Wire-free Solar Powered: Higher capacity solar panels come with security cameras to provide 1-day recording which only needs 2 hours of sunshine, 100% wireless system easy setup outdoors. This solar system will show live video and record when motion activates, with no missing details, fully protected
  • No Monthly Fees with 1TB HDD: All footage will be encrypted by the base box, which is equipped with a 1TB hard drive, ensuring there are no hidden fees. H.265 transfer, live streaming, and storage will be stable and fast, with no delays. The original system can record up to 90 days of continuous loop storage
  • 4MP Sharp & Color Night Vision: The wireless cameras are equipped with a CMOS image sensor. The WTD504 camera provides sharper, clearer, and smoother video. With color night vision, it makes nighttime as bright as daylight, offering a longer viewing range of up to 65 feet. The system can expand to a maximum of 10 channels, making it a valuable security camera solution
  • 360° No Blind Spots & Remote Viewing: Our solar security camera system supports pan (355°) and tilt (90°), providing all-around protection for your home. No matter what is happening or where you are, you can remotely view your family and property with the wireless solar camera kit
  • Install Once, Use Forever & 2.4GHz/5GHz Wifi: Designed as an outdoor wireless security camera system, you can install it anywhere you like—simply drill a couple of holes and screw it in, with no need to pay for installation. Equipped with Wi-Fi Pro technology, the solar system enhances camera signal stability and allows for longer distance transmission, keeping your home safe from any danger
  • Waterproof Design for All-Weather Protection: Our security cameras feature a high-level IP66 waterproof design, allowing them to operate normally in various harsh weather conditions. Whether it's heavy rain, snowstorms, or high temperatures, you can use these cameras with confidence. The sturdy casing and sealed structure ensure that internal components are protected from moisture and dust, providing stable and reliable monitoring to keep your home safe at all times
